# Title: DNS TXT Answer with Possible Execution Strings
# Author: Markus Neis
# Date: 2018-08-08
# Level: high
# Description: Detects strings used in command execution in DNS TXT Answer
# MITRE Tactic: Command and Control
# Tags: attack.command-and-control, attack.t1071.004
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/network/dns/net_dns_susp_txt_exec_strings.yml

answer IN ("*IEX*", "*Invoke-Expression*", "*cmd.exe*") record_type="TXT"